author: eTN Global Editor
title: Air India launches third New Delhi-London flight
text:
Click here for information and nomination Air India launches third New Delhi-London flight 
NEW DELHI, India - Air India will start a third frequency between Delhi and London from November 1, 2015. 
The flight will operate daily with a Boeing 777-200LR aircraft. 
There is already a daily flight from Mumbai making this the fourth daily flight between India and London. Oct 23, 2015
